[Mind Counter] Privacy Policy

This app does not collect or store personal information. Users only use the basic features provided by the app, and no personal information or data is stored by the app.

The information collected by the app is limited to technical information necessary for app functionality. This may include device information or error logs required for the app to operate correctly. However, personal information provided directly by the user (e.g., name, email address) is not collected.

While users may input indirect personal information such as counting targets, this information is processed solely on the local device, and it is not transmitted or shared with servers or third parties.

This privacy policy is subject to change at any time, and if any changes occur, the updated policy will be available within the app for your review.

